reviewText: Both are great scary movies and deserve rating of 5, but when I buy new, why is the case broken? Amazon has an issue with quality control, far too many things are broken or damaged that I've bought!
Waste of money. Both movies on 1 disc, and both movies only have lossy Dolby Digital stereo audio. No lossless surround audio at all.

Upon receiving from Amazon I saw those dreaded words "Mill Creek". Both of these flicks are on one disc, which I find really disappointing. I would not have purchased this if I had known.  There are no special features, no subtitles. I like the movies ok though.
No subtitle and never stated clearly , fully disappointed
Great double pack purchased just in time for Halloween.
Really good! Both very suspenseful... you'll jump out of ur seat in parts of Identity!!!
great combo as i love double features because they usually a great value
Identity is excellent, and Vacancy is good.
These two movies are awesome, don't know why people always want special features...
